Package: caliver
Type: Package
Title: CALIbration and VERification of gridded model outputs
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Claudia", "Vitolo", email = "cvitolodev@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Mirko", "D'Andrea", role = c("ctb")),
             person("Francesca", "Di Giuseppe", role = c("ctb")))
Maintainer: Claudia Vitolo <cvitolodev@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/anywhereProject/caliver
BugReports: https://github.com/anywhereProject/caliver/issues
Description: Utility functions for the post-processing, calibration and
    validation of gridded model outputs. Initial test cases include the outputs of
    the following forest fire models: GEFF and RISICO.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3)
